sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Client as client.Client
    participant Transport as Transport<br/>(stdio/HTTP)
    participant Server as server.Server
    participant Handler as ToolHandler

    Note over App,Handler: Phase 1: Initialization

    App->>Client: Initialize(ctx)
    Client->>Transport: JSON-RPC request<br/>method: "initialize"
    Transport->>Server: Parse request
    Server->>Server: Build ServerCapabilities<br/>from registered handlers
    Server->>Transport: JSON-RPC response<br/>InitializeResult
    Transport->>Client: Parse response
    Client->>Transport: JSON-RPC notification<br/>method: "notifications/initialized"
    Transport->>Server: Parse notification
    Note over Server: No response for notifications
    Client->>App: *InitializeResult, nil

    Note over App,Handler: Phase 2: Tool Discovery

    App->>Client: ListTools(ctx)
    Client->>Transport: JSON-RPC request<br/>method: "tools/list"
    Transport->>Server: Parse request
    Server->>Server: Collect registered tools
    Server->>Transport: JSON-RPC response<br/>{tools: [...]}
    Transport->>Client: Parse response
    Client->>App: []Tool, nil

    Note over App,Handler: Phase 3: Tool Invocation

    App->>Client: CallTool(ctx, "greet", args)
    Client->>Transport: JSON-RPC request<br/>method: "tools/call"<br/>params: {name, arguments}
    Transport->>Server: Parse request
    Server->>Server: Look up tool "greet"
    Server->>Handler: handler(ctx, args)
    Handler->>Handler: Execute tool logic
    Handler->>Server: *ToolResult, nil
    Server->>Transport: JSON-RPC response<br/>ToolResult
    Transport->>Client: Parse response
    Client->>App: *ToolResult, nil

    Note over App,Handler: Phase 4: Cleanup

    App->>Client: Close()
    Client->>Transport: Close connection
    Note over Transport: stdio: kill process<br/>HTTP: cancel SSE
